The paper discusses privacy-preserving aggregation of user profiles, which falls under the category of security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also involves data management and machine learning techniques, which could be categorized under databases (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of differential privacy, which could be categorized under cryptography (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
